<% content_for :page_canonical do %>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://support.texastribune.org/campaign.html">
<% end %>

<% content_for :main do %>
  <div class="splash">
    <div class="splash-wrapper">
      <div class="splash-greeting">
        <h1 class="splash-header">Fall Member Drive is going on now</h1>
        <p class="splash-info">As a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization, member drives are one of the key ways we raise funds for the Tribune’s public service journalism <em>and</em> make it free and accessible for all Texans.</p>
        <p class="splash-info">Learn more about the <a class="splash-link--yellow" href="https://www.texastribune.org/about/?_ga=2.158425146.1285863761.1507322585-1391546928.1507322585">Tribune’s mission</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="splash-donate">
        <%= partial "checkout" %>
        <p class="splash-once"><span class="weight--bold">Make a</span> <a class="splash-link--yellow" href="https://checkout.texastribune.org/donateform">one-time donation</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= partial(:campaign_desktop_nav, :locals => { :campaign_page_url => '/campaign2.html' }) %>
  </div>

  <div class="main">
    <div class="main-left">
      <div class="section">
        <h3>This Fall Member Drive, help strengthen the Tribune’s investigative tools</h3>
        <p>Public records requests, online research tools, legal fees and more. Credible accountability and investigative reporting is expensive to produce. Support these essential, ongoing expenses that help make Texas politics and policy more transparent and informed. Become a sustaining member with a recurring donation that allows the Tribune to plan budgets a few years at a time.</p>
        <p><a href="https://checkout.texastribune.org/memberform?&amount=10&installmentPeriod=yearly&_ga=2.165052026.453204924.1507322826-35454566.1507322826">Interested in becoming a student member?</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h3>Tribune membership starts at $3 per month or $35 per year</h3>
        <p>Members enjoy recognition on our <a href="https://www.texastribune.org/support-us/donors-and-members/?_ga=2.14933941.285171732.1507323227-1404484368.1507323227">donor wall</a>, discounted tickets to <a href="https://www.texastribune.org/festival/?_ga=2.215004375.1311317559.1507325008-1829771714.1507325008">The Texas Tribune Festival</a> and exclusive updates on the Tribune’s latest projects and initiatives.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h3>Circle Membership</h3>
        <ul class="info-list">
          <li>Circle Membership is a three-year commitment that backs the vital work of our journalists. <a href="/circle.html">Circle members</a> believe in supporting our public service mission so that all Texans can access our nonpartisan news, data and events at no cost.</li>
          <li>Circle Members enjoy invitations to exclusive events and special updates from CEO Evan Smith.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main-right">
      <div class="section">
        <h3>Have a question?</h3>

        <div class="contact-info">
